For phase status, frozen APIs, and hardware targets, read `.cursor/docs/PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` (or attach `@PROJECT_CONTEXT.md` in a new chat). After closing a phase milestone, update PROJECT_CONTEXT.md Sections 4 and 10 and the “Last updated” date.

